    <details class="fq"><summary>Can I take CoQ10 with other supplements?</summary><p>Yes — synergizes with omega-3, L-carnitine, magnesium, and collagen. Only caution: warfarin users should consult their doctor first.</p></details>
    <details class="fq"><summary>Is daily better than as-needed?</summary><p>Daily is essential. CoQ10 works through sustained tissue levels, not acute effects. Skipping days reduces benefits significantly.</p></details>
